  rabbit WebDAV Library</h1> <p>This is the WebDAV Library component of the Apache Jackrabbit project. This component provides interfaces and common utility classes used for building a WebDAV server or client.</p> <p>The following RFCs have been integrated:</p> <ul>  <li><a class="externalLink" href="http://www.webdav.org/specs/rfc4918.html">RFC 4918</a> (WebDAV - HTTP Extensions for Distributed Authoring, obsoleting RFC 2518)</li> <li><a class="externalLink" href="http://www.webdav.org/specs/rfc3253.html">RFC 3253</a> (DeltaV - Versioning Extensions to WebDAV)</li> <li><a class="externalLink" href="http://www.webdav.org/specs/rfc3648.html">RFC 3648</a> (Ordered Collections Protocol)</li> <li>
